Project_Title: The RNAome of the extracellular vesicles derived from THP-1 cells (human)
Project_Description:
To investigate the cargos in extracellular vesicles derived from THP-1 cells.
Overall design: Comparative gene expression profiling analysis of RNA-seq data for extracellular vesicles derived from first trimester placentae and THP-1 cells.
